\v 14 ¬∂ Pea foki atu  ªa Sisu ki KƒÅleli,  ªi he mƒÅlohi  ªoe LaumƒÅlie: pea na ªe mafola hono ongoongo ki he potu fonua ko ia kotoa pƒì.
