\v 58 ¬∂ ‚Äú ªOka ke ka  ªalu mo ho fili ki he fakamaau, ke ke fai feinga  ªi he hala, koe ªuhi ke ke hao meiate ia, telia na ªa ne  ªave koe ki he fakamaau, pea tukuange Koe  ªe he fakamaau ki he matƒÅpule pea  ªe lƒ´ koe  ªe he matƒÅpule ki he fale fakap≈çpula.
