\v 31 ¬∂ ‚ÄúPea na ªe pehƒì  ªe he  ªEiki, Saimone, Saimone, vakai,  ªoku holi  ªa Sƒìtane kiate kimoutolu, koe ªuhi ke ne fakatanga ªi \add  ªakimoutolu \add* ªo hangƒì ko e uite.
