\v 53 ‚Äå ªI he ªeku  ªiate kimoutolu  ªi he falelotu lahi  ªi he  ªaho kotoa pƒì, na ªe  ªikai mafao atu ha nima kiate au: ka ko homou feitu ªup≈ç eni, mo e mƒÅlohi  ªoe fakapo ªuli.‚Äù
